{"tid":2394662,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"sh會戰勝歸來。","createTime":"2021-02-04T10:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T12:13:39.000Z","uid":38189,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf963a97c79b5ed600c18522432398f576ff8c9","tid":2394662,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"天有光 伊朗美斯(elon musk)夥我靠岸<br />\n風有聲 財台巴打邀我作浪<br />\n唯獨我 sh gme說正道<br />\n誰在笑&nbsp;擊敗大鱷全靠sh<br />\n<br />\n又再輸錢的秘方<br />\n唯有連登財經台<br />\n華爾街紛紛告狀<br />\n拜登在銀行尋代理<br />\n為叫證卷商黑哨<br />\n念眾生 要sh救美國<br />\n<br />\n連登仔&nbsp;默然sh開拓血路<br />\nwsb 知我所想宣我盼望<br />\n無奈了 喊沽空機構太惡毒<br />\n明敵我 誓撐gme朝拜教座<br />\n<br />\n踏破關中出四方<br />\n美帝已遭拜登亡<br />\n無法矯枉的鬼角落<br />\n我教育文明倫理<br />\n時事台再誣衊我<br />\n忘掉地獄的火有多燙<br />\n<br />\nsh會戰勝歸來<br />\n淡友會掃進棺材<br />\n頌讚strong hold神聖威四海<br />\n用怨恨才同仇敵慨<br />\n股東會勇武起來<br />\n講理念 保不住價錢<br />\n<br />\n淡友戲二一招徠<br />\nsh派正氣開來<br />\n道法諸天佑蔭這變改<br />\n誓殺滅淡友全為愛<br />\n即使戰鬥鍵盤外<br />\n我N賓與GME同在。"},{"pid":"d28f8ee6ae879e9233a9d06d1eba52802158f0de","tid":2394662,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb482a2c2b8f23d0f336ec566349e4f0c155f19","tid":2394662,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416a25f659e4b1d0d63632b8c77f2bfd5b301e36","tid":2394662,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d28f8ee6ae879e9233a9d06d1eba52802158f0de","tid":2394662,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"你泰國人？"},{"pid":"0846bcc2737f46595614f28f5ce06d762f575cde","tid":2394662,"uid":74474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:32:01.000Z","msg